### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 11. CHECK TRANSACTION STATUS
###     Looks up the outcome of a debit using its reference, productId, mandateId.
###     mandateId is returned in the transaction callback payload.
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 11a. Check status — found (run after a subscribe + wait 7s for callback)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction/check-status
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "reference": "REF_2026_001",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "mandateId": "{{mandateId}}"
}

###

### 11b. Check status — not found (returns responseCode 99)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transaction/check-status
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "reference": "REF_DOES_NOT_EXIST",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "mandateId": "MANDNOTEXIST"
}


### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 12. PREAUTHORIZATION — CREATE
###     Creates a standing mandate permitting the merchant to debit the
###     customer at any point within the startDate–endDate window.
###     Returns "03" immediately. Preapproval callback fires after 2 s.
###     No money moves until /mandate/trigger-debit is called.
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 12a. Create preauth — success scenario (account ends 001)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pre-authorization/authorize
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "referenceNo": "REF_PREAUTH_001",
  "country": "GH",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01",
  "endDate": "2027-05-01",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}"
}

###

### 12b. Create preauth — endDate before startDate — expect responseCode 100
POST {{baseUrl}}/pre-authorization/authorize
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "referenceNo": "REF_PREAUTH_BAD_DATE",
  "country": "GH",
  "startDate": "2027-05-01",
  "endDate": "2026-05-01",
  "callbackUrl": "{{callbackUrl}}"
}

###

### 12c. Create preauth — invalid channel — expect 400 validation error
POST {{baseUrl}}/pre-authorization/authorize
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "channel": "VODAFONE",
  "referenceNo": "REF_PREAUTH_BAD_CHANNEL",
  "country": "GH",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01",
  "endDate": "2027-05-01"
}

###

### 12d. Duplicate reference — expect responseCode 104
POST {{baseUrl}}/pre-authorization/authorize
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "merchantId": "{{merchantId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "referenceNo": "REF_PREAUTH_001",
  "country": "GH",
  "startDate": "2026-05-01",
  "endDate": "2027-05-01"
}


### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 13. PREAUTHORIZATION — TRIGGER MANDATE DEBIT
###     Triggers a specific debit against an existing mandate.
###     Uses the mandateId returned in the preapproval callback (not preApprovalId).
###     Returns "03" immediately. Transaction callback fires after 5 s.
###     Replace MANDATE_ID_FROM_CALLBACK with the actual value.
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@preAuthMandateId = MANDATE_ID_FROM_CALLBACK

### 13a. Trigger mandate debit — success scenario (account ends 001)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mandate/trigger-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "mandateId": "{{preAuthMandateId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "debitAmount": "200.00",
  "narration": "Monthly insurance premium",
  "referenceNo": "REF_MAND_DEBIT_001",
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "currency": "GHS"
}

###

### 13b. Trigger mandate debit — mandate not found
POST {{baseUrl}}/mandate/trigger-debit
Content-Type: application/json
x-transflowId: {{transflowId}}
x-key: {{apiKey}}
x-country: {{country}}

{
  "mandateId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "debitAmount": "200.00",
  "narration": "Monthly insurance premium",
  "referenceNo": "REF_MAND_DEBIT_002",
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "currency": "GHS"
}


