### 16. PREAUTHORIZATION — CANCEL
###     Cancels an active preauth. All three fields (debitAccount, channel,
###     country) must match the original record to confirm ownership.
###     Replace PREAPPROVAL_ID_FROM_CALLBACK with the actual value.
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@preApprovalId = PREAPPROVAL_ID_FROM_CALLBACK

### 16a. Cancel preauth — happy path
POST {{baseUrl}}/pre-authorization/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
