  "preApprovalId": "{{preApprovalId}}",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "debitAccount": "0241234001",
  "channel": "MTN",
  "country": "GH"
}

###

### 16b. Cancel — mismatched details — expect responseCode 100
